SOLUTION EXPLANATION 

Graph explanation for the different countries and a call for action to policy makers. 

 

Our analysis and visualisations have shown measurable changes in crop yields over time. 

From the analysis carried out on the data obtained from FAOSTAT (Food and Agriculture Organisation of the United Nations) and NASA POWER Data Access Viewer, using power query and PowerBi, the following insights were drawn, 

